    <reapack name="ReaTitles - Offline Transcription.lua" type="script" desc="Offline faster-whisper transcription with live progress">
      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[
# ReaTitles Offline Transcription

Transcribes selected audio locally and creates grouped subtitle items.

Requires Python 3, faster-whisper, FFmpeg, a local Whisper model and ReaImGui for the progress window.
        ]]></description>
      </metadata>
